{"tid":1219433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下 次 遊 行 記 得 帶 區 旗","createTime":"2019-06-13T20:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T22:53:11.000Z","uid":177955,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"81e3accb9d281718f49be8e3220023b0c0de57b5","tid":1219433,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:23:30.000Z","msg":"先唔好理抽氣扇嗰五粒星咩中共旗<br />\n今次嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標</span>係政府撤回修例</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>破壞社會</span><br />\n遊行抗爭係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個途徑</span></span><br />\n區旗上面嗰<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">洋紫荊係代表<span style=\"color: red;\">我哋屋企</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最重要係區旗可以吸引到一啲廢老嘅注意<br />\n等佢哋認為大家係<span style=\"color: red;\">忠於香港</span> 為香港好<br />\n得輿論者勝</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">此外 當黑警打壓嘅時候 區旗係代表佢哋<span style=\"color: red;\">背叛香港</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既代表我哋又合法 唔會有位畀廢老入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b48a0496cf9f4aa2f19ac73eef5d459394d2342","tid":1219433,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:23:40.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b7d61fc0705d5e56a341ee80a52be1d3f331f3","tid":1219433,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:23:50.000Z","msg":"push🇭🇰"},{"pid":"a3f04cb12a45a9fa8c99fa4c508b3f94102a1e35","tid":1219433,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:24:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"96d70e44ec3e8f5da258d888923ba4903972f0fd","tid":1219433,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:24:22.000Z","msg":"Pu